text: diniki karanamemitante, vastavaniki vari vaddaku vari pravaktalu, spastamaina sucanalu tisukoni vaccinappatiki, varu: "Emi? Maku manavulu margadarsakatvam cestara?" Ani palukutu satyanni tiraskarinci marali poyaru. Mariyu allah kuda varini nirlaksyam cesadu. Mariyu allah svayam samrd'dhudu, sarvastotralaku ar'hudu
